1. create an angular project named Milestone3
2. create a Json file for employee add all the required fields
3. configure the json server and watch the employee json file
4. create a service layer and implement all the service methods given in the problem statement
5. create components as mentioned in the problem statement
6. call out the service in the component using dependency injection
7. implement the logical methods in order to communicate with the front end
8. create a directive "custome Directive " that will hold the color which can be reused
9. design your admin html
10. created a route in navbar to admin and user
